    "is_free": false,
    "description": "这个人是如何死的？！利用你的推理技能找出答案！在这款第一人称侦探游戏中，你将扮演一名法医，通过几个真实而又奇怪的案件。调查现场，收集线索，搜集情报，检查尸体并进行尸检。<br><br>这个游戏将包含大约15个关卡，需要解决神秘的死亡案件。 <strong>所有的死亡案件都基于真实事件。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/c9d9c4cb7c11286ff34509ce12ccaee8.avif?t=1737768439\" width=616 height=68 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阶段1：检查现场</h2><br>当你到达现场时，最好从在场的人那里收集信息。例如，警察是各自领域的专家，习惯了这些情况。然而，不要将他们的信息视为绝对真实。作为科学家，你必须保持开放的思维！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/33d03fbc4a1086e5f3f2c005bf064025.poster.avif?t=1737768439\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/33d03fbc4a1086e5f3f2c005bf064025.webm?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/33d03fbc4a1086e5f3f2c005bf064025.mp4?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与其直接看尸体，不如检查整个现场。一些元素可能提供关键线索。一个细节可以改写整个故事！例如，你的紫外线灯可以揭示被清洁过的血迹！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/5338deddfe4f6886b9c4bb12798319d1.poster.avif?t=1737768439\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/5338deddfe4f6886b9c4bb12798319d1.webm?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/5338deddfe4f6886b9c4bb12798319d1.mp4?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>最后，去检查尸体，扫描它，检查它；在前往尸检室之前，你可能已经对发生的事情有了一些想法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/e932ea491429d6d3ae83f4bbea38e5cc.poster.avif?t=1737768439\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/e932ea491429d6d3ae83f4bbea38e5cc.webm?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/e932ea491429d6d3ae83f4bbea38e5cc.mp4?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阶段2：尸检</h2><br>在尸检阶段，要识别可能表明问题的器官细节。器官不会撒谎关于发生的事情。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/d7dbbec39a4180da62557a3e759f3a74.poster.avif?t=1737768439\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/d7dbbec39a4180da62557a3e759f3a74.webm?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008440/extras/d7dbbec39a4180da62557a3e759f3a74.mp4?t=1737768439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
